ranges.description: ranges of allowable IDs for fsGroup

type.description: strategy used to generate the SELinux context

allowHostPorts.description: allow the use of the host ports in the containers

allowedCapabilities.description: capabilities that are allowed to be added

items.description: capabilities that are allowed to be added

items.description: groups allowed to use this SecurityContextConstraints

items.description: capabilities that will be dropped by default and may not be added

items.description: seccomp profiles allowed to be used by pods and containers

items.description: users allowed to use this SecurityContextConstraints
